title: What are some popular songs with nonsensical lyrics? - Quora

response.answer_text: Don’t Look Back In Anger by Oasis is complete nonsense; even Noel Gallagher admits the words are meaningless. However, play it to a bunch of drunken brits over 30 and they’ll all join in.
